Did you catch me on TV this morning where I shared about the differences of flour and baking tips on @ch8sg variety show【健康那些事- Get Fit With Me】together with hosts @dasmondkoh , @kym_ng and @iamfeliciachin ?
.

This meaningful program is specially tailored during COVID-19 to educate and entertain audience especially elderly when everyone has to stay home.
.
In this show, you can see some of my pastries which I’ve baked using Blue Jacket flour. I would like to thank @innobakesg for sponsoring the flour for the filming too.
@innobakesg Thank you for your great support! 🙏
@baking_taitai of course! we enjoy your content either ways too :)

@eatandtravelwithus please, no celebrity... just sharing what I enjoy best! 😄🍰🧁🍞🥖🍪

介绍超详细 果然专业 👍👍👍听起来光是面粉就需要了解很多知识呢

@vegkitchensg Thank you! It’s not my first appearance on TV. Screen debut was 3 years ago when I demonstrated how to make homemade bak kwa and filming was done at home. You can hop over to my blog or my YouTube channel to take a look. 😉

@vegkitchensg no worries and thanks for the compliment! 😄
Amazing Cheryl! Congrats on your screen debut! 🙌
@doublev_baking Thank you! Hope you find it informative! 😊
@noveltydream Thank you for the thumbs up!!! 🙏
@killgwen keto baking using almond flour, coconut flour, chia seed flour etc. 😉

@lindesiree Thanks Desiree for your kind words! 😊
